	•	route_decision
	•	lookup_context
	•	llm_draft_prompt
	•	draft_cdi
	•	approved_cdi
	•	execution_log
	•	result_artifact

This makes debugging possible.

If something goes wrong, Beast can show exactly where:
	•	bad transcript
	•	bad parser route
	•	bad lookup grounding
	•	bad LLM draft
	•	bad UI rendering
	•	bad execution

